Taiwo Adeleke, a nurse working with the University of Medical Sciences in Ondo State, who was declared missing on Sunday evening after threatening to commit suicide, has been found. It was learnt that Adeleke, who works at the Emergency and Accident Unit of the government-owned hospital, was tracked down and rescued in the early hours of Monday. See Also






